6.title: PopWrapped TV Exclusive Doreen Taylor at the House of Blues
6.plot: Popwrapped had the chance to sit down with Country singer Doreen Taylor at her stripped down show at The House of Blues on May 1st. Doreen is about to embark on her "Magic" tour. She gives us a bit of insight to her influences, the first timed she preformed and what makes her stand out above the crowd.

7.title: PopWrapped PRESENTS: PopCovers: Clarity - Jodi Good (Zedd and GLEE Cover)
7.plot: In the first edition of our PopCovers series, meet 22 year old NYC Singer/Songwriter Jodi Good. PopCovers is a series where newly discovered talent, as well as some very familiar faces, cover songs EXCLUSIVELY for PopWrapped! Jodi Good is a Berkley Vocal alumnae. Her debut EP, "Definitely Different," will be out this July. Jodi has a powerful voice and the ability to immediately capture you with it.

25.title: PopWrapped TV Exclusive First Look Green Day's American Idiot in LA!
25.plot: AMERICAN IDIOT, crafted from the iconic Grammy Award-winning album by Green Day, chronicles the frustration, anger, and dreams of a lost generation of young Americans as they struggle to find meaning in a post 9/11 world. This rock-infused presentation is produced for glory struck by Topher Rhys, Jamie Lee Barnard, and Juliana Scott who most recently produced the award-winning, Ovation nominated Los Angeles revival of BARE. Before that, the grunge-inspired SPRING AWAKENING aligned with Brittany Snow's Love is Louder.
